    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of dependable performance and refined aesthetics. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity and interior excellence meet our rigorous standards for quality. Representing a premier choice for the discerning driver, this automobile remains in commendable condition and is prepared for immediate delivery. We invite you to acquire a high-caliber machine that offers both prestige and long-term reliability.",
      "price": 33800.0,
